data.description: This inviting corner-lot home features 3 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a stylish kitchen with granite countertops and an island for casual dining. The integrated speaker system sets the mood throughout the house. The converted garage offers a versatile space, while the outdoor kitchen and grill make entertaining a breeze. The home is meticulously maintained and includes a 240-volt outlet for charging your smart car. It's the perfect blend of indoor comfort and outdoor entertainment. Seller will contribute towards closing cost
